  <description><![CDATA[<p><span>The well-equipped Levi Cottages have recently been refurbished to a high standard and are in a very convenient central location.  The cottages are located just 150 metres from the main resort amenities and 450 metres walk from <a data-udi="umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c}" title="Levi">Levi's</a> well stocked supermarket.  Guests who would prefer to have meals included rather than self-cater can pre-book half board, with a breakfast and 3 course evening meal taken at K5 Hotel 150m away. </span></p>
<h2><span>Eat in or dine out</span></h2>
<p><span>The Levi Cottages are self catered apartments, so you can cook tasty meals from the comfort of your own cottage or head out for dinner and sample some of the lovely restaurants Levi has to offer. Alternatively there is the option to upgrade to half board. Each day you can make the most of the extensive breakfast buffet which has a range of hot and cold options, for dinner you can enjoy a three course buffet style dinner.</span></p>
<h2>Traditional cottages</h2>
<p>Each of the cottages is furnished in a traditional style, yet has all of the amenities needed for a break in <a data-udi="umb://document/2da7ac9814d44a75af6718b02ca02250" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2da7ac9814d44a75af6718b02ca02250}" title="Lapland/Finland">Lapland</a> including a well equipped kitchen,  a TV, and a drying cupboard. Cosy up in front of the fire after a day of exploring Levi or embrace Finnish traditions and unwind in the private sauna - it is the perfect place to warm up and relax after a day on the slopes. </p>
<h2>Great location</h2>
<p>The Levi Cottages have a convenient location just a short walk to the resort centre where you can find plenty of bars, restaurants and souvenir shops, plus the well stocked supermarket. If you are heading to the slopes, there is a ski bus which runs regularly <span>between the ski area and the main accommodation areas, so you can make the most of the snowy fells and wonderful landscape. </span></p>]]></description>
