  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Studio + mezzanine apartments </strong>are around 35m²+mezz and sleep two to four people. These apartments have twin beds in the living room plus a comfortable mattress beds in the mezzanine</p>
<p><strong>One bedroom + mezzanine apartments</strong> are around 45m²+mezz and sleep two to six people with one twin bedroom, four comfortable mattress beds in a large mezzanine, and a open plan living room and kitchenette.</p>
<p>Cottages are located in several buildings. Beds to be made up on arrival. Final clean included</p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Cottage facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Sauna</li>
<li>Drying closet</li>
<li>Fireplace (For 2023/24 firewood will be €15 per apartment, payable locally)</li>
<li>Fully equipped kitchen with an oven, microwave, toaster, fridge, kettle, coffee-maker and dishwasher </li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Iron and ironing board</li>
<li>One bathroom with shower</li>
<li>Cots and high chairs available (pay locally)</li>
<li>One linen and towel set included, per person per week</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>]]></roomsDescription>
